          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780984755707" href="/book/show/13184491-avogadro-corp">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer573221398" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11221254717279115440">Great book from a first-time novelist. Plausible creation backstory for a strong AI that leads to the most basic drive for all living things: survival. I enjoyed this book so much that I bought the sequel immediately after I finished.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


