<li class='cover' id='bookCover_15808659'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15808659-kill-decision"><img alt="Kill Decision" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1365395383l/15808659._SY160_.jpg" />
